---
import ExternalLink from '@/components/external-link.astro'
import LogoName from '@/components/logo-name.astro'
import Logo from '@/components/logo.astro'
import MainLayout from '@/layouts/main.astro'
import { TWITTER_URL } from 'src/constants'
---

<MainLayout
  title='Colophon'
  desc='This page displays technical information about nikolovlazar.com. It lists the technologies, the ui design, and other services that are used.'
>
  <div class='hero-grid'>
    <h2>
      The source code can be found on{' '}
      <ExternalLink href='http://github.com/nikolovlazar/v2-nikolovlazar.com'>
        Github
      </ExternalLink>
    </h2>
    <p>
      This website is designed by <ExternalLink
        href='https://twitter.com/Ivana1991_'
      >
        Ivana Rangelova Nikolova
      </ExternalLink>
      and developed by <ExternalLink href={TWITTER_URL}>
        Lazar Nikolov
      </ExternalLink>. It's built with just <ExternalLink
        href='https://astro.build'
      >
        Astro
      </ExternalLink> and Pure CSS. It is deployed on <ExternalLink
        href='https://vercel.com'
      >
        Vercel
      </ExternalLink>. Completely Open Source ðŸ’œ.
    </p>
    <h2>Typography - IBM Plex Serif</h2>
    <p>
      For the typeface Ivana decided to use the <ExternalLink
        href='https://fonts.google.com/specimen/IBM+Plex+Serif?query=ibm+plex'
      >
        IBM Plex Serif
      </ExternalLink> font. It's downloaded from Google Fonts, converted into woff2,
      and hosted within the website for performance reasons.
    </p>
    <h2>Design & Colors</h2>
    <p>
      The design inspiration for this website is 80s computer and science
      manuals, like the 1984 Macintosh Manual and the 1975 NASA Graphics
      Standards Manual. The light color used is the <ExternalLink
        href='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cosmic_latte'
      >
        Cosmic Latte
      </ExternalLink> color. It is the average color of the universe.
    </p>
  </div>
  <hr />
  <div class='typography'>
    <div class='typeface regular'>
      <div class='examples'>
        <span class='uppercase'>ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ</span>
        <span class='lowercase'>ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ</span>
        <span class='symbols'>1234567890&lt;%$^&*()=-</span>
      </div>
      <p class='name'>IBM Plex Serif Regular</p>
    </div>
    <div class='typeface semibold'>
      <div class='examples'>
        <span class='uppercase'>ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ</span>
        <span class='lowercase'>ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ</span>
        <span class='symbols'>1234567890&lt;%$^&*()=-</span>
      </div>
      <p class='name'>IBM Plex Serif Semibold</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <hr />
  <div class='colors-and-logo'>
    <div class='colors-grid'>
      <div class='cosmic-latte'>Cosmic Latte</div>
      <div class='rich-black'>Rich Black</div>
      <div class='fuschia-blue'>Fuschia Blue</div>
    </div>
    <p class='cosmic-latte-paragraph'>
      light coming from galaxies (and the stars within them) â€“ alongside all the
      visible clouds of gas and dust in the Universe â€“ when averaged, would
      produce an ivory color very close to white. They named this color 'cosmic
      latte'. The rich black color is a complementary to cosmic latte. The
      fuschia blue is a brand color Lazar picked long time ago.
    </p>
    <div class='logo-grid'>
      <div class='rich-black-cosmic-latte'>
        <LogoName color='var(--colors-cosmic-latte)' />
      </div>
      <div class='cosmic-latte-fuschia-blue'>
        <LogoName color='var(--colors-fuschia-blue)' />
      </div>
      <div class='cosmic-latte-rich-black'>
        <LogoName color='var(--colors-rich-black)' />
      </div>
      <div class='rich-black-fuschia-blue'>
        <LogoName color='var(--colors-fuschia-blue)' />
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class='logo-paper-grid'>
      <Logo />
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>

<style is:global>
  .hero-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr;
    margin-top: 40px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    column-gap: 24px;
    row-gap: 40px;
  }

  .hero-grid h2 {
    font-size: var(--fontSizes-xl);
  }

  .typography {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    row-gap: 40px;
    margin-top: 40px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .typography .typeface {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: end;
  }

  .typography .typeface.regular .examples * {
    font-family: var(--font-regular);
  }

  .typography .typeface.semibold .examples * {
    font-family: var(--font-semibold);
  }

  .typography .typeface .examples {
    font-size: var(--fontSizes-3xl);
  }

  .typography .typeface .name {
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .typography .typeface .examples .uppercase {
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .typography .typeface .examples .lowercase {
    text-transform: lowercase;
  }

  .colors-and-logo {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    row-gap: 64px;
    margin-top: 40px;
    margin-bottom: 80px;
  }

  .colors-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    width: 100%;
  }

  .colors-grid > div {
    height: 104px;
    border: 1px dashed #9b9b99;
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: var(--font-semibold);
  }

  .colors-grid .cosmic-latte {
    background: #fff8e7;
    color: var(--colors-rich-black);
  }

  .colors-grid .rich-black {
    background: var(--colors-rich-black);
    color: #fff8e7;
  }

  .colors-grid .fuschia-blue {
    background: var(--colors-fuschia-blue);
    color: #fff8e7;
  }

  .cosmic-latte-paragraph {
    width: 66.6%;
    align-self: end;
    text-align: right;
  }

  .logo-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
  }

  .logo-grid div {
    height: 185px;
    border: 1px dashed #9b9b99;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .rich-black-cosmic-latte {
    background: var(--colors-rich-black);
    color: #fff8e7;
  }

  .cosmic-latte-fuschia-blue {
    background: #fff8e7;
    color: var(--colors-fuschia-blue);
  }

  .cosmic-latte-rich-black {
    background: #fff8e7;
    color: var(--colors-rich-black);
  }

  .rich-black-fuschia-blue {
    background: var(--colors-rich-black);
    color: var(--colors-fuschia-blue);
  }

